ail Stakes at Ellerslie in the spring before a break. Her jump-out win here was soft as you like, and she will be ready to rumble fresh. Her winning chances soar on a wet track. 8. TRES MAGNIFIQUE turned heads first-up at Bendigo, crunched into $1.35 and absolutely demolished a 0-62 field by 7 lengths. She mixed it with stakes-class fillies last prep and often had no luck, so now that she is stronger, expect her to go right on with the job. 3. MAGNABELLE ROYALE is unbeaten from 3 starts, and she resumed with an effortless Cranbourne win, putting a margin on them without being fully extended. She drops in weight, and she could again take some pegging back. 11. ESPANA resumes with some strong form lines from last prep. She is drawn to receive a cosy run, and having Jamie Melham in the saddle is a strong lead fresh. Use the market as your best guide.\",\"runners\":[2,8,3,11],\"exclusive\":true}","ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[8,3,13,6]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[13,11,12,8]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,6,4,10]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,7,11,4]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,4,5,7]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[8,4,6,3]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,4,8,5]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"SAN